<title>StateToViewportPolicyUpdateSystem</title><para>Queries the current <computeroutput>GameState</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>MatchState</computeroutput> from the session, then uses the configured <computeroutput>StateToViewportPolicy</computeroutput> to determine which viewports should be active. The resulting viewport IDs are stored in the session for use by the rendering system.</para>
<para><bold>Registration:</bold> <programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="normal">systemRegistry.add&lt;StateToViewportPolicyUpdateSystem&gt;(</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>Phase::Pre,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::move(policy)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
